      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Nothing to Sneeze At!",
        "Client": "Sniffling Scholar",
        "Description": "Ah...ah...ACHOO! Sorry... *sniff* Ugh...\r\nCaught a cold somewhere between the\r\nFrost Islands and Lava Caverns...\r\nIf I\u0027m ever gonna study Bisha...AH...\r\nACHOOO! *sniff* Bishaten, I\u0027ll need your\r\nhelp. In return, I\u0027ll teach you some\r\nposes that vividly express my misery...",
        "Target": "Hunt 2 Bishaten",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Sortez les mouchoirs !",
        "Client": "\u00C9rudit enrhum\u00E9",
        "Description": "Aa... aa... ATCHOUM ! Pardon...\r\n*renifle* J\u0027ai attrap\u00E9 froid entre\r\nl\u0027Archipel de glace et les Cavernes\r\nde lave... Si tu m\u0027aides \u00E0 \u00E9tudier le\r\nBisha... aa... ATCHOUM ! *renifle*\r\nBishaten, je t\u0027apprendrai des poses\r\nqui retranscrivent bien mon \u00E9tat...",
        "Target": "Chasser deux Bishaten",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Ricerche a suon di starnuti",
        "Client": "Erudito raffreddato",
        "Description": "E... E... ECCI\u00D9! Scusa. Uff, non\r\n\u00E8 salutare viaggiare tra le Isole\r\nghiacciate e le Caverne laviche.\r\nSe dovessi mai studiare un Bisha...\r\nE... ECCI\u00D9! Bishaten, in cambio\r\ndel tuo aiuto ti insegner\u00F2 delle\r\npose che esprimono la mia pena.",
        "Target": "Caccia 2 Bishaten",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Wer niest denn da?",
        "Client": "Schniefender Gelehrter",
        "Description": "Ha-HATSCHI!... *schn\u00FCff* Hab\r\nmich zwischen Frostinseln und\r\nLavah\u00F6hlen erk\u00E4ltet. Wenn ich\r\nje den Bisha-Ha-HATSCHI!\r\nstudieren will, brauche ich\r\ndeine Hilfe. Daf\u00FCr zeige ich\r\ndir wehleidige Posen.",
